      "side": 1,
      "message": "I misunderstood, you are correct. We need a mechanism to differentiate old v.s. new behavior. Here are some quick metrics that I will add to the e2e tests.\n\nMetrics from perf test listing 10 snapshots, 50,000 times:\n\n\nWithout diskSize\n------------------------------------------ benchmark \u0027snapshot\u0027: 1 tests -------------------------------------------\nName (time in ms)              Min      Max    Mean  StdDev  Median     IQR   Outliers       OPS  Rounds  Iterations\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\ntest_list_snapshot_perf     5.7377  15.5937  6.5834  0.5405  6.4500  0.4697  8683;3774  151.8983   50000           1\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nWith diskSize\n------------------------------------------ benchmark \u0027snapshot\u0027: 1 tests -------------------------------------------\nName (time in ms)              Min      Max    Mean  StdDev  Median     IQR   Outliers       OPS  Rounds  Iterations\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\ntest_list_snapshot_perf     5.4284  23.3697  7.1573  0.7071  7.0727  0.6291  9267;3255  139.7169   50000           1\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------",
